<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Breslau</head><p>Makulierter Entwurf des folgenden Briefs.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_125" id="62v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_125_r1l24">Der Stat cʒu Preſʒlaw</ab>
</del></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_125_r1l25"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Mertein wagner <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burger / vvie er nü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l26">cʒu dem nehſtvergangen ſant 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>walp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> tag </del> Johans tag cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l28">Sünvvenden / etvvieuil kuppfers / v̈mb einen 
<del rend="strikethrough">ewr mitburger </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_125_r1l27">bey ew cʒu preſʒlaw </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l30">genant hans von 
<del rend="strikethrough">la </del> lewn gekaufft 
<del rend="strikethrough"> h </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_125_line_1576739550862_581">hab </ab></add> der Jm das für 
<add><ab facs="#facs_125_r1l29">gut </ab></add> Smolnicʒer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l31">kuppfers <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Nu hat derſelb Mertein wagner </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l32">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger den Meiſtern hıe bey vns ver kuppfer </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l33">
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu kauffen <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / d </del> Nu ſind etliche Meıſter hie 
<del rend="strikethrough"> den </del> die von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l35"> <expan>de<ex>m</ex>ſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> Mertein wagner kuppfer 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_125_r1l34"><expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> für vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l36"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns geſagt bey Jren eyden / vvie daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l38">ſich daſſelb kuppfer 
<add><ab facs="#facs_125_r1l37">das ſie von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Merteın wagner <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> das Jn derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> alſo <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l39">weder <expan>ſlah<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Smyden noch arbeiten laſſen wölle / als ſıch <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></del>
<pb facs="#facs_126" id="63r"/><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_126_r1l2">vormals <expan>gewönlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Smölnicʒer kuppfer geſmidt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l3">gearbeit hab laſſen / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ Jr dem <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l4">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger ewr günſtige <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweıſen wöllet </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l5">
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ Jm darümb von dem ewren ein genüge geſchehe </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l6">
<del rend="strikethrough">Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / </del> Ob der <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l7">von <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> kuppfers wegen ichts an ewr weiſheit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l8">bringen würde / daʒ Jr Jm <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l9">darynne ewr günſtige <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweiſen wöllet / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l10">Als etc das wöllen etc </ab>
</del>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_125" id="62v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Der stat czu Preszlaw </del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> uns hat
                                                  <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Mertein Wagner,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, wie er nü
                                                  czu dem nehstvergangen sant Johans tag czu
                                                  sünwenden etwievil kuppfers ümb einen <add>bey ew
                                                  czu Preszlaw</add> genant Hans von Lewn gekaufft
                                                  <add>hab</add>, der im das für <add>gut</add>
                                                  Smolniczer kuppfers <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                  hab; nu sind etliche meister hie, die von
                                                  <expan>de<ex>m</ex>selbe<ex>n</ex></expan> Mertein
                                                  Wagner kuppfer
                                                  <add><expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan></add>
<expan>habe<ex>n,</ex></expan> für uns
                                                  <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns gesagt bey iren
                                                  eyden, wie daz sich dasselb kuppfer, <add>das sie
                                                  von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Mertein Wagner
                                                  <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab,</add> weder
                                                  <expan>slah<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> smyden noch
                                                  arbeiten lassen wölle, als sich
                                                  <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
</del><pb facs="#facs_126" id="63r"/><del rend="crossout">vormals <expan>gewönlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                  Smölniczer kuppfer gesmidt und gearbeit hab
                                                  lassen. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> ob der
                                                  <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger von
                                                  <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> kuppfers wegen
                                                  ichts an ewr weisheit bringen würde, daz ir im
                                                  <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen darynne ewr
                                                  günstige <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweisen
                                                  wöllet, als etc.; das wöllen etc. </del></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
